C) Default Gateway:
Route table is needed:
From which IP we need to connect to Which server.

# ip route add 192.10.1.0 via 192.10.2.1

If the A,C wants to connect to internet.
#  ip route default via 192.10.2.1
#  ip route default via 192.10.1.1


Note:
Basically to reach different network, route table is required.
If set default gateway like 0.0.0.0 in the Gateway then the system within internal network not required to crate a table.

# ip link
